snippet.title: I Had To Do This | Indie Horror Game Devlog
snippet.description:
I made a massive change a few weeks ago... why did I do it? Was it worth it?

UPDATE: I can't be bothered recording sections of this again so here we go: I did NOT get the funding after all. Kickstarter page will be launching soon, so make sure to click the link below to get notified when it does!

►Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wearenotalone/we-are-not-alone-1/

► Join the mailing list: http://stasisboothgames.com/newsletter/

Wishlist We Are Not Alone:
►Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2249440/We_Are_Not_Alone/
►Itchio: https://stasisboothgames.itch.io/we-are-not-alone
►Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/we-are-not-alone-demo-7c9a44


► Visit Deadeguard on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DeadeGuard98
